Summer staples: sunglasses, mini fan, and SUNSCREEN ☀️
The Laneige Hydro UV Defense EX SPF 50+ is your skin’s daily defense against UV damage! This ultra-light, non-greasy sunscreen offers broad-spectrum SPF 50+ protection without leaving a white cast. Enriched with Glycerin, Aloe Vera, Centella Asiatica, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), and Ascorbyl Glucoside (a Vitamin C derivative), it keeps your skin hydrated, calm, and radiant all day long. Also perfect under makeup and suitable for all skin types.
